cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DB, cs.CL, cs.CR

This paper deals with knowledge representation and reasoning, which is a core topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It specifically focuses on hybrid knowledge bases, which combine description logics (DLs) and nonmonotonic rules, making it relevant to logical reasoning (cs.LO) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses update operators, which are important in natural language processing (cs.CL) and cybersecurity (cs.CR).
